Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:45.38,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru will...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:48.88,Sai,,0,0,0,,start walking the path to the divine move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.67,Sai,,0,0,0,,It won't be me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:52.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,but Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.72,Sai,,0,0,0,,Is there no way that I can escape this fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:59.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,that God has in store for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:08.11,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(300,115)}The Sixtieth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:08.11,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Farewell Hikaru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:13.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:14.86,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Is it just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:18.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It looks like the stain has faded\Nsince the last time I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:29.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.55,Sai,,0,0,0,,There is no way for me to escape fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:42.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I guess it was always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I guess it was just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma and I are going to see a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A play!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have an overnight job tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Two days and one night at a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there are supposed to\Nbe around 150 customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to play tutoring games and stuff there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A few other pros are going to be there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you came all this way,\Nyou'll want to play, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, I'll give you a thousand\Nyen if you beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.27,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.36,Sai,,0,0,0,,Let's go home... and play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:39.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,You can play Grandpa any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can play any time we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I hardly ever see Grandpa, I\Nshould play him when I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:51.96,Background,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:02.31,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'm going to disappear soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your stupid worries again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous. You've been here for a\Nmillennium already, how can you disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:23.37,Background,,0,0,0,,You'd better not be trying to make me feel sorry\Nfor you so that you can have your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:27.41,Background,,0,0,0,,You've been acting really selfish lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.54,Background,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just watch me play Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for, Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:42.72,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru can...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru can...
