Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:32.52,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs7.5\1c&H1C0F1A&\bord0\shad0\blur0\fscy160\frz2\pos(100,323)}Registration
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shindou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:36.44,Background,,0,0,0,,Your room is 303, you're with\NNagai-kun and Yokoi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Master Ogata is here, too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I should stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want him giving me trouble about Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:56.59,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H000000&\blur0.5\fad(1835,0)\bord0\shad0\fscy75\frz5\fs9.5\t(0,8865,1,\fs12)\move(472,68,405,96,0,8865)}Japanese Go Institute {\fs11\fscy75\t(0,8865,1,\fs15)\fscy70}GO SEMINAR
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ogata is a solid player\Nwho plays all kinds of styles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but his opponent Haruko-san is a forceful player.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Master Ogata played here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In my opinion, this is a rather questionable move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But who knows what Master Ogata\Nwill say to me later if I deride it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:26.62,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs8.5\1c&H010300&\bord0\shad0\blur0\fad(1335,0)\fscy140\frz1\move(231,360,-46,360)}Shindou Hikaru first dan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this Sagari isn't too useful right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you have other plans with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can escape if you really want to,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.18,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still playing Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! M-Master Ogata!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't have to be so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you out drinking with Master Ogata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We celebrated his Jyudan title.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Wow, he looks drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me play Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master Ogata! I told you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:33.81,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:35.94,Sai,,0,0,0,,Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Stop being selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:41.19,Sai,,0,0,0,,It will be alright if he's this drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.44,Sai,,0,0,0,,It won't amount to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:44.78,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:51.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. It doesn't look like he'd\Nbe able to play very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.95,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But are you alright with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:57.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,I probably won't have any opportunities\Nto play a real game against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.75,Sai,,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of a game it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:05.46,Sai,,0,0,0,,I will be if it will let me respond to the\Ndetermination he showed at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:07.72,Memory,,0,0,0,,Let me play him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll let him play you for a bit to congratulate\Nhim on his Jyudan title.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ogata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Play me, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in playing\Nhim when he's this drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll settle for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:49.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Will he really be able to play Go when he's this drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll sober up a bit after playing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:59.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why do you look so down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Respond to me at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll let you play today for Master Ogata's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but you've been really disagreeable lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.12,Sai,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:24.21,Sai,,0,0,0,,Why is it not me, but Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.09,Sai,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.13,Sai,,0,0,0,,Why is Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,Why is it only Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.89,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'm going to disappear! But Hikaru is going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:49.86,Sai,,0,0,0,,I can't contain my jealousy towards\NHikaru for having an existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.45,Sai,,0,0,0,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:09:59.95,Sai,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,want to leave Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:18.31,Sai,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to leave Torajirou either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.27,Sai,,0,0,0,,Torajirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:27.23,Sai,,0,0,0,,said to me, while on the brink\Nof death from the plague...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.15,Sai,,0,0,0,,'Sorry... Sai...'
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.79,Sai,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:44.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.67,Sai,,0,0,0,,want to leave him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.42,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.64,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll be going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for turning the lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can play without the lights on by the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're drinking more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm drunk either way, it won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I may not be able to play very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it won't be strange at all if I crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't challenge me when I'm this drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge me in an official match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have high expectations of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The day of your new first dan series match...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kuwabara and I made a\Nbet that day on who would win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet on Master Touya because\NMaster Kuwabara bet on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is I wanted to bet on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I can trust what a drunk tells me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You little punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, I am drunk for a change today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like I'm finally starting to feel the\Njoy of at last having become Jyudan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We did have quite a ruckus with\NMaster Touya's retirement...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I did become Jyudan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but the world won't recognize me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,until I successfully defend the title next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, I'm going to\Nrun all the way to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.26,Background,,0,0,0,,Well Shindou, like I said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me play Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Settle for playing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:20.90,Background,,0,0,0,,Alright, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixteen... you're going first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:25.09,Background,,0,0,0,,You messed up on an easy life or death problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.89,Background,,0,0,0,,Master Ogata, you must be really drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about my mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You played in such a strange\Nplace on the top right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and threatened a large cluster of my stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up playing poorly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and my game fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you had a little too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:58.34,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I guess letting him play Sai didn't pay off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:03.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But then again, it would have been troublesome\Nif he had realized that Sai was playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:08.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess there's little chance of\Nthat happening if he's this drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:16.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I feel kind of sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Such solid play...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:26.91,Background,,0,0,0,,I was playing Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be really drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I guess he was somewhat satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:42.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll go home first thing tomorrow,\Nso that I won't see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In the actual game, White played here\Nto destroy Black's eye shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but first White should have connected\Nto the center like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and waited for Black to play here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Good morning Master Ogata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He went home first thing this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he doesn't have any more work to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:46.61,Background,,0,0,0,,I slept a little on the bullet train, but I'm still tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.00,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm about to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I wish you'd worry about my health a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep after one game, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.88,Sai,,0,0,0,,A hundred forty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,Torajirou lent his body to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:59.89,Sai,,0,0,0,,If Torajirou existed for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.65,Sai,,0,0,0,,then I existed for Hikaru's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.19,Sai,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:13.66,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru exists for someone else as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.62,Sai,,0,0,0,,And that someone will, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.54,Sai,,0,0,0,,be there for another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:24.04,Sai,,0,0,0,,A millennium becomes two,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:27.42,Sai,,0,0,0,,built up slowly person by person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:54.57,Sai,,0,0,0,,The long path leading to the divine move...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.67,Sai,,0,0,0,,My part in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.54,Sai,,0,0,0,,is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.13,Sai,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.05,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.81,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:22.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.27,Sai,,0,0,0,,Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.15,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.11,Sai,,0,0,0,,It was fu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
