Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:23.96,Background,,0,0,0,,Mai-chan, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:23.02,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(209,0)\3c&HFA20F6&\4c&HFA20F6&\fscx100\fscy95\bord1\shad0.5\move(750,349,318,349)}Can you take advantage of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:31.53,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,959)\3c&HFA20F6&\4c&HFA20F6&\fscx100\fscy95\bord1\shad0.5\pos(318,349)}Can you take advantage of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:24.94,Background,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:26.81,Background,,0,0,0,,It's Atari, so I'll capture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:28.47,Background,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:30.73,Background,,0,0,0,,That's Atari, so I'll connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:31.88,Background,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:33.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Yup! That's right!
