Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:37.24,Background,,0,0,0,,Now these four White stones can't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to hurt White's territory a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:43.05,Background,,0,0,0,,But had you connected here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:47.07,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs27\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(1126,626)\fscx200\t(0,970,1,\fscx100)\3c&HFA20F6&\4c&HFA20F6&\fscy85\bord1\shad0.5\pos(320,363)}If you respond wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:47.17,Background,,0,0,0,,White would have responded here, and his\Nterritory would have been very large.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:51.95,Background,,0,0,0,,The correct move for White would have\Nbeen to move here at this point.
